itemDescription.value: George Cross recipient in World War II

British locomotive engineer and designer of the LMS Ivatt Class 2 2-6-2T’s and Ivatt Class 2 2-6-0’s,Ivatt Class 4 2-6-0’s, and designer of the Caprotti Black 5 4-6-0’s and designer of LMS 1000 and 1001 Diesel Locomotives (First Maine Line Diesel)
Welsh minister, founder of the Elim Pentecostal Church
English baritone and voice teacher in Canada
English divine, Fellow and Chaplain of New College, Oxford
